{
  "stanzas": [
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "Throned upon the awful tree,"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "Lamb of God, Your grief we see."
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "Darkness veils Your anguished face;"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "None its lines of woe can trace."
        },
        {
          "number": 5,
          "text": "None can tell what pangs unknown"
        },
        {
          "number": 6,
          "text": "Hold You silent and alone."
        }
      ],
      "number": 1
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "Silent through those three dread hours,"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "Wrestling with the evil powers,"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "Left alone with human sin,"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "Gloom around You and within,"
        },
        {
          "number": 5,
          "text": "Till th’appointed time is nigh,"
        },
        {
          "number": 6,
          "text": "Till the Lamb of God may die."
        }
      ],
      "number": 2
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "Hark, that cry that peals aloud"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "Upward through the whelming cloud!"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "You, the Father’s only Son,"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "You, His own anointed one,"
        },
        {
          "number": 5,
          "text": "You are asking- can it be?"
        },
        {
          "number": 6,
          "text": "“Why have You forsaken Me?”"
        }
      ],
      "number": 3
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "Lord, should fear and anguish roll"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "Darkly o’er our sinful soul,"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "You, who once were thus bereft"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "That Your own might ne’er be left,"
        },
        {
          "number": 5,
          "text": "Teach us by that bitter cry"
        },
        {
          "number": 6,
          "text": "In the gloom to know You nigh."
        }
      ],
      "number": 4
    }
  ],
  "title": "Throned Upon the Awful Tree"
}
